      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Rumbling Tummy, Rumbling Thunder",
        "Client": "Hinoa the Quest Maiden",
        "Description": "Bunny Dango just taste so much\r\nbetter after a quest. Would you\r\ncare to join me for the quest part?\r\nAn Astalos in the Jungle sounds\r\nlike the perfect pre-dango workout!\r\nI can\u0027t wait for my victory dango!\r\nMmmHmm ~\u266A I can taste \u0027em now!",
        "Target": "Hunt an Astalos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La jungle des \u00E9clairs",
        "Client": "Hinoa la qu\u00EAtatrice",
        "Description": "Les dango-lapins sont bien\r\nmeilleurs apr\u00E8s une qu\u00EAte.\r\nQue dirais-tu de m\u0027aider\r\nd\u0027ailleurs ? Un Astalos dans\r\nla Jungle, y\u0027a rien de mieux\r\npour s\u0027ouvrir l\u0027app\u00E9tit avant\r\nde d\u00E9guster de bons dango !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Astalos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Giungla di fulmini",
        "Client": "Hinoa la missionatrice",
        "Description": "I dango a coniglietto hanno\r\nun sapore migliore dopo una\r\nmissione. Vuoi venire con me\r\ne affrontarne una? Un Astalos\r\nnella giungla \u00E8 una ginnastica\r\nperfetta prima dei dango.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Astalos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Magenknurren, Donnergrollen",
        "Client": "Hinoa das Quest-M\u00E4del",
        "Description": "Dango schmecken nach einer\r\nQuest gleich doppelt so gut.\r\nBegleitest du mich auf dem\r\nQuest-Teil? Ein Astalos ist\r\ndoch das perfekte Workout,\r\num Dango abzutrainieren, oder?\r\nIch kann sie schon schmecken!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Astalos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Est\u00F3mago atronador",
        "Client": "Hinoa la gestora de misiones",
        "Description": "Los dango saben mucho mejor\r\ndespu\u00E9s de una misi\u00F3n.\r\n\u00BFQuieres acompa\u00F1arme en mi\r\nnueva misi\u00F3n? \u00A1No hay nada\r\nmejor que un Astalos en la\r\nJungla para abrir el apetito y\r\nzamparse unos buenos dango!",
